<section class="oe_container">
   <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
        <h2 class="oe_slogan" style="color:olive"><b>BOM Product Cost Price</b></h2>
        <h3 class="oe_slogan" style="color:green;"><b>Cost Price for BOM Products</b></h3> 
        <p class="oe_mt32" style="color:olive;">
This module allow you to view BOM cost Price on Product which has BOM and Show Total Cost on BOM Form.</p>
        
        <p style="color:CRIMSON;">
                <b>Main Features:</b>
        </p>
        <p style="color:olive">
            <ul>
                <li style="color:olive;">Allow you to view BOM total cost price on Product Template.</li>
                <li style="color:olive;">Show BOM Total cost for Product Template BOM.</li>
                <li style="color:olive;">Allow you to view BOM total cost price on Product Variant.</li>
                <li style="color:olive;"> Show BOM Total cost for Product Variant BOM.</li>
                <li style="color:olive;">Allow you to select BOM on product template and variant if you want to see cost for specific BOM on product form. This is for case where there are multiple BOM for single product and product variants. So system will allow you to select BOM on product form and show price for that BOM only.</li>
                <li style="color:olive;">For more details please see Video in Live Preview.</li>
                <li style="color:olive;">V11 Video Link : <a href='https://youtu.be/yK4ZHqXXY8c' target="_blank">https://youtu.be/yK4ZHqXXY8c</a></li>
                <li style="color:olive;">V12 Video Link : <a href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5wRFRywN0zI' target="_blank">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5wRFRywN0zI</a></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
</section>

